{"tid":801071,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple市值月內增1400億美元　相當於一間NIKE或IBM","createTime":"2018-08-31T10:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T02:43:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2654c0bb6c8edd45b823585b4348ffb5bbe7f0","tid":801071,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，自本月較早時市值突破1萬億美元以來，蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)股價持續創新高，如周三(8月29日)收市股價剛剛再創新高，這也是8月份公司股價第12次創新高。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司股價8月份漲幅勢將超過15%，是自2012年2月份以來漲幅最大的一個月。當年，蘋果公司市值為5056.7億美元，現在市值已突破1萬億美元，周三晚收市最新市值升至10,770億美元，與2012年2月時相比增長110%。<br />\n<br />\n僅8月至周三止，蘋果公司市值增長約1,400億美元，這個增長已相當於一整間NIKE(市值為1,325億美元)或IBM(市值為1,347億美元)的市值。<br />\n<br />\n過去3個月，蘋果公司股價累計上漲17%，是表現第二好的道指成分股，僅次於製藥廠商默克。<br />\n<br />\nWashington Crossing Advisors投資組合經理摩根蘭德(Chad Morganlander)看好蘋果公司的未來，尤其是高速增長的服務業務。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，未來5年蘋果公司能提高服務業務在營收中的比重，市盈率會更高，因為服務業務屬於可預期、利潤率更高的業務。<br />\n<br />\n在最近一個財季，蘋果公司服務業務營收達到創記錄的95億美元，比上年同期增長31%。目前，服務業務在蘋果公司營收中的佔比為13%。<br />\n<br />\n摩根蘭德並預期，未來12個月蘋果公司股票總收益率將達到6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180830/bkn-20180830173140289-0830_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180830%2Fbkn-20180830173140289-0830_00842_001.html&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f5bbd7a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180830/bkn-20180830173140289-0830_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nAPPLE真係超勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159aa16111de8af437718d2a507a9120bd0407f7","tid":801071,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"邊間市值最高<br />\nNIKE真係估唔到咁高"},{"pid":"92349266c8f2132729b0c0c93d073a3c90357421","tid":801071,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"159aa16111de8af437718d2a507a9120bd0407f7","tid":801071,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"邊間市值最高<br />\nNIKE真係估唔到咁高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:39:08.000Z","msg":"宜家最高咪apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81af73153ba76f82cfda892c19a38b92a0218e42","tid":801071,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"Amazon 先係王道"},{"pid":"a2e4ecdeb8e72db0b5e4baf07cf3ce51a2ca4de8","tid":801071,"uid":39508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"159aa16111de8af437718d2a507a9120bd0407f7","tid":801071,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"邊間市值最高<br />\nNIKE真係估唔到咁高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"全球龍頭運動品牌喎 <br />\n分分鐘名牌都無佢咁值錢<br />\n係d覺得人地係賣體育用品唔夠高級先睇人唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d0214c3b4750434233035fdaf646b7a3e03aae","tid":801071,"uid":30615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"159aa16111de8af437718d2a507a9120bd0407f7","tid":801071,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"邊間市值最高<br />\nNIKE真係估唔到咁高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"估唔到咁細就真，仲細過中移動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbfbfd1aff3997b66dbef02249d17e5b80a9fe3","tid":801071,"uid":71463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"159aa16111de8af437718d2a507a9120bd0407f7","tid":801071,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"邊間市值最高<br />\nNIKE真係估唔到咁高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"好高咩？ 僅8月至周三止嘅升幅（1400億）就等如一整Nike <br />\n<br />\nApple :10000億<br />\nNike : 1400億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde60aca0219e32cbcb7bfced464563ccd490ff3","tid":801071,"uid":25002,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re